title: 3 and Out - Rodgers' New Green Bay Reality; NFL Draft Rounds 1-3 Reaction; Biggest Winners/Losers
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Rodgers' New Green Bay Reality; NFL Draft Rounds 1-3 Reaction; Biggest Winners/Losers
description:
In this episode, Middlekauff reacts to the Packers picking Jordan Love in the first round, and why it sends a message to Aaron Rodgers that the new regime isn't beholden to him like Mike McCarthy and former GM Ted Thompson. He also goes around the league with reaction to rounds 1-3 of the Draft, and his biggest winners/losers. Follow John on twitter @JohnMiddlekauff and go to theherdnow.com to find the latest content.
